        "Description": "The problem is simple, stress.  And even more than that, it&apos;s stress on a tropical island.  The combination of the stress and weather means these five need to release tension and cool off.  And what better way to release tension than the sweet release of death making you go limp?  Of course, 47 would need to cool off with a swim afterwards.",
